(Yes, it's true, we really did spend a wonderful twelve months in Hawaii and decided to leave for other pastures.  Yes, Steve) show
0 281.6 moveto
10 f0
(takes the prize for finding us, in January, a wonderful apartment with swimming pool and lanai, right on the ocean.  Yes, we) show
0 270.6 moveto
10 f0
