(Alright it almost seems like we're behaving like people with careers.  Steve's great contribution this year was to deplete the) show
0 679.3 moveto
10 f0
(world's paper resources by co-authoring a book based on his PhD thesis \(yes, please rush out and buy a copy!\) and) show
0 668.3 moveto
10 f0
(publishing a number of significant papers on software engineering, re-engineering and program understanding \(more) show
0 657.3 moveto
10 f0
(explanation will cost you\).   Together with some of his co-conspirators he's also started a company that has yet to sell) show
0 646.3 moveto
10 f0
(anything or make any money, but what an idea!  In September, his post-doctoral year at Uni. of Hawaii came to a tearful) show
0 635.3 moveto
10 f0
(close and he ) show
51.9 635.3 moveto
10 f0
(spent the next few months based at CSIRO in Canberra but collaborating with the SEI in Pittsburgh and) show
