(In early November, we acquired a new addition to the family ... a very tall chestnut) show
156.1 412.1 moveto
10 f0
(equine called Mr McEnroe.  So far he hasn't displayed the temperament of his) show
156.1 401.1 moveto
10 f0
(namesake but is keeping Kirsty busy riding early in the morning and doing stablework) show
156.1 390.1 moveto
10 f0
(late into the evening.  If all goes according to plan, they'll start competing at low-level) show
156.1 379.1 moveto
10 f0
(eventing \(that's jumping and dressage to the non-horsey\) competitions early next) show
156.1 368.1 moveto
10 f0
(year.   Steve spent a few hours in Sept/Oct re-acquainting himself with the joys of) show
156.1 357.1 moveto
10 f0
(coaching and playing hockey in Canberra, and we've also been doing a little hiking, a) show
0 344.3 moveto
