(Come January 6th, everybody must observe a moment of silence as we start the unpleasant experience) show
88.2 274.5 moveto
10 f0
(of living in different hemispheres.  Come January, Steve starts a new job as a member of the technical) show
88.2 263.5 moveto
10 f0
(staff at the Software Engineering Institute in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.  Much to our surprise Pittsburgh) show
88.2 252.5 moveto
10 f0
(boasts tree-lined streets, green hills and 19th century style architecture rather than belching steel mills,) show
88.2 241.5 moveto
10 f0
(coal mines and stooped sooty inhabitants, but still.  The SEI is a US government institution which) show
88.2 230.5 moveto
10 f0
(provides advice on building and changing software to US govt. and industry.  Impressive, huh!  Kirsty) show
88.2 219.5 moveto
10 f0
(will spend her days at the National Museum annoying people with difficult questions and accumulating) show
88.2 208.5 moveto
10 f0
(obscure government documents so that she can write ) show
302 208.5 moveto
10 f0
(some esoteric and very intelligent papers.  This) show
0 197.5 moveto
10 f0
(phase will hopefully wrap up in about September when she can relocate to Pittsburgh,) show
0 186.5 moveto
10 f0
(lock herself in a room and produce a lot of words that can be summarized as Ph.D. ) show
0 175.5 moveto
10 f0
(Before all this starts, however, we will enjoy a Christmas week at the South Coast with) show
0 162.7 moveto
10 f0
(the Wehners.  Watch out jellyfish!) show
